comment.author: 32162360@N00
comment._content: Oops! 1890 guess wrong. According to the Australian Heritage website - - (which is under revision), there were " Ornamental iron fence and gates cast at an Albury foundry and erected in 1884 " - www.environment.gov.au/cgi-bin/ahdb/search.pl?mode=place_... So date of this image is 1880-84.
